<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Jaadooghar OTP</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f7fafc;
            padding: 16px;
            font-family: sans-serif;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 24rem;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 0.375rem;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 16px;
        }

        .heading {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .message {
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: #4a5568;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .otp {
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .otp-code {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            color: #2f855a;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 24px;
            color: #718096;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .footer strong {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="content">
        <div class="heading">
            <h1>Hey {{name}}</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="message">
            <p>Thanks for choosing Jaadooghar. Use the following OTP to complete your sign-up process. Do not share this code with others.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="otp">
            <h1 class="otp-code">{{otp}}</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Have a great day</p>
            <p><strong>Regards:</strong> Jaadooghar.com</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>

</html>
